Contains the grammar definition

Each grammar declaration contains a list of rules and tokens.
  - Grammar declaration are [ruleName]
  - Rules are {ruleName}
  - Tokens are (tokenName)

What precedes each grammar line must be a tabbed list of lines expanding undefined rules (with no previous grammar declaration)
declared in the previous grammar line in the order they appear.

_____

grammar definition:
_____

[top] -> {declaration} {top} | {assignment} {top} | {directive} {top} | {function} {top} | e

  [declaration] -> {type} (IDENTIFER)
    [type] -> {data} | (IDENTIFER)
    [data] -> (INT), (SIGNED_INT_32), (UNSIGNED_INT_32), (BOOl), (STRING), (CHAR)
  
  [assignment] -> {declaration} (EQUAL) {assignmentExpression} | (IDENTIFER) (EQUAL) {assignmentExpression}
    [assignmentExpression] -> {assignmentExpressionTarget} {operator} {assignmentExpression} | {assignmentExpressionTarget} 
      [assignmentExpressionTarget] -> (IDENTIFER) | {literal} | {functionCall} 
        [literal] -> (STRING_LITERAL) | (INTEGER_LITERAL)
        [functionCall] -> (IDENTIFER) (LEFT_PARENTHESIS) {parametersCall} (RIGHT_PARENTHESIS)
          [parametersCall] -> {prametersCallList} | e
            [prametersCallList] -> {passable} | {passable} (COMMA) {prametersCallList}
              [passable] -> (IDENTIFER) | {literal}
      [operator] -> (PLUS) | (MINUS) | e 


  [directive] -> (LEFT_BRACKET)(RIGHT_BRACKET)

  [function] -> {type} (IDENTIFER) (LEFT_PARENTHESIS) {parametersDeclaration} (RIGHT_PARENTHESIS) {directive} {primaryExpression}
    [parametersDeclaration] -> {parametersDeclarationList} | e
      [parametersDeclarationList] -> {type} (IDENTIFER) | {type} (IDENTIFER) (COMMA) {parametersDeclaration}
    [primaryExpression] -> {declaration} {primaryExpression} | {assignment} {primaryExpression} | {controlflow} {primaryExpression} | e
      [controlflow] -> {conditionalBranch} | {functionCall}
        [conditionalBranch] -> (IF) {conditinalExpression} {continuedCondition}
          [conditinalExpression] -> (LEFT_PARENTHESIS) {booleanExpression} (RIGHT_PARENTHESIS) {primaryExpression} 
            [booleanExpression] -> {assignmentExpression} {booleanExpressionList}
              [booleanExpressionList] -> {booleanConcat} {booleanExpression} | e
                [booleanConcat] -> (AND) | (OR)
          [continuedCondition] -> (ELSE) {conditinalExpression} | (ELIF) {conditinalExpression} {continuedCondition} | e